verbose_text: Apoptosis induced by the different lipoplexes was measured using an Annexin V-FITC/PI Apoptosis Detection Kit. LH-Lip / siBCL-2 induced significantly less apoptosis and necrosis in LO2 cells but significantly more BXPC-3 cell necrosis than did N-Lip / siBCL-2.
evidence: Apoptosis Detection Kit. LH-Lip/siBCL-2 induced significantly less apoptosis and necrosis
